<h2 id="anazon-gift-card">Anazon Gift Card</h2>

<p>Amazon accepts all major forms of payment such as credit card, debit, and other methods of payment. For more information, see <strong>the Accepted Payments</strong> page on the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=GFBWMNXEPYVJAY9A" target="_blank"><strong>Amazon Help Site</strong></a>.</p>

<p>Amazon Gift cards function as a temporary method of payment. Users either purchase or receive an Amazon Gift Card for a set value, such as $25, that allows them to purchase almost anything from the Amazon Web Store. Some restrictions do apply. For more information, see the <strong>Considerations and Restrictions</strong> section.</p>
